DVS128 example:
C: gcc -std=c11 -pedantic -Wall -Wextra -O2 -o dvs128_simple dvs128_simple.c -D_POSIX_C_SOURCE=1 -D_BSD_SOURCE=1 -lcaer
C++: g++ -std=c++11 -pedantic -Wall -Wextra -O2 -o dvs128_simple dvs128_simple.cpp -D_POSIX_C_SOURCE=1 -D_BSD_SOURCE=1 -lcaer

DAVIS example:
C: gcc -std=c11 -pedantic -Wall -Wextra -O2 -o davis_simple davis_simple.c -D_POSIX_C_SOURCE=1 -D_BSD_SOURCE=1 -lcaer
C++: g++ -std=c++11 -pedantic -Wall -Wextra -O2 -o davis_simple davis_simple.cpp -D_POSIX_C_SOURCE=1 -D_BSD_SOURCE=1 -lcaer
